</s2>
</content1></s-1>
<s-1 id="RM00000137Z013X_01_0037" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00003BC00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE LOWER INSTRUMENT PANEL SUB-ASSEMBLY
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a clip remover, remove the 2 clips &lt;A&gt;.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the 2 bolts &lt;B&gt;, 4 nuts &lt;C&gt;, screw &lt;D&gt; and 2 screws &lt;E&gt;.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Disconnect the hood lock control cable, fuel lid lock control cable, DLC3 and ash receptacle light.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Disconnect the connectors and detach the clamps.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Detach the 2 guides and remove the lower instrument panel.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>for Automatic Air Conditioning System:</ptxt>
<ptxt>Disconnect the room temperature sensor.</ptxt>
